<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink314">
<l>avirtoṭi koṭpak kaḻutupuka vayarak</l>
<l>karuṅkaṭ kākkaiyoṭu kaḻukuvicum pakavac</l>
<l>ciṟukaṇ yāṉai yāḷvīḻttut tiritaru</l>
<l>nīḷiṭai yaruñcura meṉpanan</l>
<l>tōḷiṭai muṉinar ceṉṟa vāṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>They say that the path traveled by the man</l>
<l>who  despised our shoulders and waist –</l>
<l>lies through the difficult desert with a long way,</l>
<l>where demons, [their] shining bracelets whirling, hunt for food,</l>
<l>black-eyed crows and vultures screech in the sky,</l>
<l>and small-eyed elephants roam about killing men.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
